name: Matchcup
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Launched in 13/12/2022 by a team based in United States of America, MATCH token is the native currency of the blockchain-based MatchCup ecosystem. All interactions with and within the ecosystem take place via MATCH token, which serves as the ecosystem's Utility Token.
